{"id": "1351472561426399264", "channel_id": "1351472561426399264", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "感謝各位守密人的支持！\n《忘卻前夜》OST：扭曲瘋人之院，今日發佈～歡迎大家收聽、下載及分享～如果有基於OST的二次創作，也歡迎分享給我們！ （二創請遵照同人規則，OST內容請勿商用）\n\n忘卻前夜OST：扭曲瘋人之院\n追獵，奔逃，凝固的母愛，跨越生死的相擁。\n\n作曲：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\n規劃：B.I.A.V. Studio\n\n——◆——◆—— ◆◆◆ ——◆——◆——\n\nThank you for your support!\n\n《Morimens》OST：《Twisted Asylum》 was released today. \nWelcome everyone to listen, download and share. If you have secondary creations based on the OST, please also share them with us!\n (Please follow the rules of the fandom for secondary creations, and do not use the OST content for commercial purposes)\n\n《Morimens》OST：《Twisted Asylum》 \nHunting, running, solidified maternal love, and an embrace that transcends life and death.\n\nComposer：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\n\nPlanning：B.I.A.V. Studio", "timestamp": "2025-03-18T08:29:27.790000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🔥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}, {"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1351472561799565332", "filename": "-.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 379939, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1351472561426399264/1351472561799565332/-.jpg?ex=69ccd767&is=69cb85e7&hm=140bfb5181549bde7c0b1563c177f3409655096dfdf149b7233343cbf91677bf&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1351472561426399264", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "《忘卻前夜》OST：扭曲瘋人之院", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1351472778376777728", "channel_id": "1351472561426399264", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "1.未落的雪-Unfallen Snow-\n\n無論她如何落筆，都只能在日記上留下黑色的殘缺。\nNo matter how she wrote, she could only leave a black mark on the diary.", "timestamp": "2025-03-18T08:30:19.515000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-03-18T08:33:49.601000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1351472777965731861", "filename": "1.-Unfallen_Snow-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 30102854, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1351472561426399264/1351472777965731861/1.-Unfallen_Snow-.wav?ex=69ccd79b&is=69cb861b&hm=78d0ff54dc2eb3daf793ab994a1bfe0e2ad0d555d3c9b35073fcd0a3dc460312&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1351472561426399264", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "《忘卻前夜》OST：扭曲瘋人之院", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1351472823646031968", "channel_id": "1351472561426399264", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "2.午後童話-Afternoon Fairy Tales-\n\n那時，母親翻動著書頁，為孩子說童話故事。\n午後的溫度跨越時間，細細流淌在這片狹窄的時空。\nAt that time, the mother turned the pages of the book and told fairy tales to her children.\nThe temperature of the afternoon transcended time and flowed gently in this narrow space and time.", "timestamp": "2025-03-18T08:30:30.308000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-03-18T08:33:43.659000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1351472823314677770", "filename": "2.-Afternoon_Fairy_Tales-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 22353034, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1351472561426399264/1351472823314677770/2.-Afternoon_Fairy_Tales-.wav?ex=69ccd7a6&is=69cb8626&hm=e76151237ab23a7be28a5ba65f6894631a2f9f19276b72acf131d022f72ef920&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1351472561426399264", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "《忘卻前夜》OST：扭曲瘋人之院", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1351472895649382441", "channel_id": "1351472561426399264", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "3.極地祭壇-Polar Altar-\n\n詭異的密語在空氣中迴盪，黑色的黏液將祭品吞噬，舊日的存在期待著神明的歸來。\nStrange whispers echoed in the air, black mucus devoured the sacrifice, and the old existence looked forward to the return of the gods.", "timestamp": "2025-03-18T08:30:47.475000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-03-18T08:33:38.155000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1351472895640997940", "filename": "3.-Polar_Altar-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 36394072, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1351472561426399264/1351472895640997940/3.-Polar_Altar-.wav?ex=69ccd7b7&is=69cb8637&hm=c775fc5e9498fa05a51f960dbd90a43a366abf5b2b8bfb339ebba7bbee6bc977&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1351472561426399264", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "《忘卻前夜》OST：扭曲瘋人之院", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1351472984916754522", "channel_id": "1351472561426399264", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "4.對立的正義-Clashing Justices-\n\n當立場和意志發生碰撞，人類往往只會堅信自己的準則。\n對多數人而言，自己所相信的，便是唯一的正義。\nWhen positions and wills collide, humans tend to only believe in their own principles.\nFor most people, what they believe in is the only justice.", "timestamp": "2025-03-18T08:31:08.758000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-03-18T08:33:32.068000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1351472984468230155", "filename": "4.-Clashing_Justices-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 50451016, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1351472561426399264/1351472984468230155/4.-Clashing_Justices-.wav?ex=69ccd7cc&is=69cb864c&hm=b89e123796fd2f094c10b09f81901d863708839dd5bdd41181e6c94915854603&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1351472561426399264", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "《忘卻前夜》OST：扭曲瘋人之院", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1351473054903173252", "channel_id": "1351472561426399264", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "5.不期的重逢-Unexpected Reunion-\n\n相見來的過早，真相來的太遲，被殘酷現實撕碎的心靈，正在幼小的雙手中漸漸癒合。\n跨越風雪互相追逐的兩人，終於在超越時間的狹縫間，相擁而泣。\nThe meeting came too early, the truth came too late, and the heart torn by the cruel reality was gradually healing in the young hands.\nThe two who chased each other across the wind and snow finally hugged and cried in the narrow gap beyond time.", "timestamp": "2025-03-18T08:31:25.444000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-03-18T08:33:24.879000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1351473054596726794", "filename": "5.-Unexpected_Reunion-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 7956524, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1351472561426399264/1351473054596726794/5.-Unexpected_Reunion-.mp3?ex=69ccd7dd&is=69cb865d&hm=a5ff9aa387cdd87f634ea80328052d919b95dce9fd190049d3a5f553edba325f&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1351472561426399264", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "《忘卻前夜》OST：扭曲瘋人之院", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1351473230417756182", "channel_id": "1351472561426399264", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "6.撕裂維度而來-Tearing Through Dimensions-\n\n束縛怪物的枷鎖已被破壞，無法殺死，無法逃離的獵手，來了。\nThe shackles that bound the monster have been broken, and the hunter who cannot be killed or escaped has come.", "timestamp": "2025-03-18T08:32:07.290000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1351473230829064222", "filename": "6.-Tearing_Through_Dimensions-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 20728348, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1351472561426399264/1351473230829064222/6.-Tearing_Through_Dimensions-.wav?ex=69ccd807&is=69cb8687&hm=80102c268764d302e104dc0d646667dc84bc4fddbfa73e266fe42d56776eb52c&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1351472561426399264", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "《忘卻前夜》OST：扭曲瘋人之院", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1351473353395011656", "channel_id": "1351472561426399264", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "7.悲愴的綻放-Bittersweet Blossom-\n\n深淵中綻放的潔白花，牢牢擋在眾人身前。\n“即使是這樣，那也是我唯一的媽媽。”\n“把我的媽媽——還給我！”\nThe white flower blooming in the abyss is firmly blocked in front of everyone.\n\"Even so, she is my only mother.\"\n\"Give my mother back to me!\"", "timestamp": "2025-03-18T08:32:36.610000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1351473353239826442", "filename": "7.-Bittersweet_Blossom-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 44227300, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1351472561426399264/1351473353239826442/7.-Bittersweet_Blossom-.wav?ex=69ccd824&is=69cb86a4&hm=0a652aacb1cca983c3b485b7f8b5181e4aa3e45b6babf168012cca874f2cc8bd&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1351472561426399264", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "《忘卻前夜》OST：扭曲瘋人之院", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1351473501218799667", "channel_id": "1351472561426399264", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "8.因果的怪物-Monster of Cause and Effect-\n\n時間在嘶吼，時間在咆哮，時間在追逐三度淪為獵物之人。不要嘗試逃跑，因為結果早已註定。\nTime is screaming, time is roaring, time is chasing the person who has become prey three times. Don't try to escape, because the result is already determined.", "timestamp": "2025-03-18T08:33:11.854000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1351473500849963009", "filename": "8.-Monster_of_Cause_and_Effect-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 44799594, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1351472561426399264/1351473500849963009/8.-Monster_of_Cause_and_Effect-.wav?ex=69ccd847&is=69cb86c7&hm=260d8c05a1098eec6bd29a21fbccee04f779a3948bb5f1b52ad1c47549408d69&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1351472561426399264", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "《忘卻前夜》OST：扭曲瘋人之院", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1351473532978073633", "channel_id": "1351472561426399264", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "9.永恆囚籠-Eternal Prison-\n\n在這扇連時間都能囚禁的大門背後，是一位母親為了守護自己心愛的女兒，所做的最後抉擇。\n“我愛你，莉莉。”\nBehind this door that can even imprison time, is the final decision made by a mother to protect her beloved daughter.\n\"I love you, Lily.\"", "timestamp": "2025-03-18T08:33:19.426000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1351473532655243316", "filename": "9.-Eternal_Prison-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 33796752, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1351472561426399264/1351473532655243316/9.-Eternal_Prison-.wav?ex=69ccd84f&is=69cb86cf&hm=f47e0b94213e54188d3356a7cba5901e7a1378100fbcfb581f88e922a412b268&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1351472561426399264", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "《忘卻前夜》OST：扭曲瘋人之院", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
